Validation:
	* Stochastic Local Search
		1) C random;
			1.a) gamma random;
			1.b) check (C,gamma) with 2 possible gamma step in both directions;
			1.c) stop if no gain;
		2) Check on 2 possible C step in both directions starting from 1);
		3) Stop if no gain;
	* Fast simple (grid which stop iterations if the precision decrease)
	* Find suitable parameters for C and gamma (C should be the max of the value assumed in the validation)

